pyradio (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release
  * GTK4-based internet radio player
  * RadioBrowser API integration for station discovery
  * Support for Dutch and international radio stations
  * Favorites management with persistence
  * ICY metadata display (now playing, bitrate)
  * GStreamer-based audio playback
  * Offline station caching
  * Search and filter functionality

 -- PyRadio Developers <pyradio@example.com>  Sun, 30 Nov 2025 14:00:00 +0100
